Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.76,0:00:01.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Darkness and Light!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.82,0:00:03.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Into the chaos of\nthe Feudal Era,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.63,0:00:05.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Sacred Jewel brings a\n{\i1}group of strangers together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.03,0:00:09.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}500 years across time,\ntheir destinies are controlled{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.13,0:00:11.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}by the few remaining shards\nof the Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.77,0:00:13.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Feudal Fairy Tale:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.13,0:00:14.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.74,0:00:17.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}At the border between this world\nand the next, the shard sleeps.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:19.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}At its only entrance, the Gate to the\NLand of Fire,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.21,0:00:21.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}giant sentries stand guard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.81,0:00:24.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And even here,\NNaraku's trap awaits us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.89,0:02:16.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The spot where Inuyasha\nand I first met...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:21.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although that was actually during\nthe Feudal Age.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:25.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Sacred Tree!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:28.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so glad!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:29.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This must be close to home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:35.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A....boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:58.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it all began right here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.48,0:03:09.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You have it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:12.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You must have {\i1}it....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:13.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let me go, you disgusting thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:16.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give me the Sacred Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:21.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't you even handle a weak\nthing like the Centipede Demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:24.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You....just spoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.73,0:03:26.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.23,0:03:29.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let....go....of....me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:30.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Owweee!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.63,0:03:32.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let go of ME!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.47,0:03:33.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Hand it over!\N- Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:35.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:37.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can you pull out this arrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:39.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:44.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm asking if you can pull out\nthis arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:48.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I... I don't understand a thing\nthat's happening!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.32,0:03:53.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:58.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:09.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:11.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up, old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:15.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.99,0:04:33.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I hadn't been attacked\nby that demon...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.66,0:04:37.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I hadn't met Inuyasha\non that day...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:39.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wouldn't have to stress\nout during tests,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.77,0:04:44.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and Grandpa wouldn't have to\nagonize over my feigned illnesses.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:48.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sis, you're up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:49.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, I had something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:53.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Before, she'd still be dead to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:56.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mom, is my lunch ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:58.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, all done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.29,0:05:00.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.12,0:05:00.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.79,0:05:02.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, {\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:07.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't forget to ask everyone\nhow it all tasted, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:08.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:13.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Junior high students have it tough\nenough with just their studies.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:16.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:16.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:18.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Morning, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:21.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get with it! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:22.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:27.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again today, I'm setting out\ninto the Feudal Age.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:43.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And again today...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.83,0:05:47.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome! Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:50.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:53.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Inuyasha! Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.61,0:05:56.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll do my best again to\nfind the Sacred Jewel shard{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:58.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and continue our journey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:17.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Have you noticed, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:18.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.54,0:06:24.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Saimyosho are watching us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:26.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.64,0:06:30.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just making sure that we're\nheading towards the Realm of Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:37.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Old Myoga, are you sure you\ndon't know
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:40.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,any other way to get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:44.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I do not know any other way\nto get to the grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:46.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wanna {\i1}know....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:48.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,where the entrance is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:53.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:57.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hakudoshi is headed towards\nthe Mountain in the Realm of Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:07:00.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's supposed to be a gate there
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:03.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that leads to the border between\nthis world and the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Mountain in the Realm of Fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.08,0:07:07.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this, Kagura?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:09.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why have you come to\ntell us this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:10.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.52,0:07:12.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'd have to ask Hakudoshi that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:27.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems the Saimyosho plan to\nlead us to the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:33.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, but if they've come to\nshow us the {\i1}way....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:36.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Perhaps it means that Hakudoshi\ndoesn't have the power
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:38.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to pass through the gate on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:39.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we're talking about the usual Naraku,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.01,0:07:42.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sure he has something\nup his sleeves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:45.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But this is Hakudoshi, not Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:49.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, {\i1}Hakudoshi....who{\i0} was created\nby Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:53.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Geez! Who cares which it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:55.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All we have to do is get there first
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:08:00.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and get a hold of the Sacred Jewel\nshard that's at the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:02.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Such a simpleton.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:06.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And that's just like Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:08.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:18.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So this is the Realm of Fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:19.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:21.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And it certainly looks\nlike the land of fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:27.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those {\i1}are....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:28.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're luring us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:32.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go after 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:33.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hachi, go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.78,0:08:47.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.72,0:08:50.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's kinda creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:51.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uh-huh....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:55.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah, really feels like\nthe entrance to a grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.96,0:08:56.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:08:58.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.63,0:09:01.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:17.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura, Inuyasha and his friends\nmade it to the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:20.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You sure about letting them\ngo in first?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.52,0:09:24.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't the Sacred Jewel shard\non the other side of that gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:27.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Of course, we'll get the shard first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:32.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In order to do that, Kagura,\nyou'll have to do your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:36.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Humph....{\i0} So you want the last laugh, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:38.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're just like Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:40.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmmm....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:47.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:50.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, there must be\na huge gate in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:52.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}K-Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:53.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Shippo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:57.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,D-Don't those rocks look\nlike the faces of demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:09:59.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:02.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And they seem to be\nincreasing as we {\i1}proceed....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:05.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe they're just paving\nstones to the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:06.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:07.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:07.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:10.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! I think we've finally\nmade it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:23.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This {\i1}is....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:26.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There really is a gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.65,0:10:28.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So nice and simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:31.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And there aren't any guards around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:33.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everyone, get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:38.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll break apart the gate\nwith my Wind Scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:39.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You want to pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.73,0:10:40.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.56,0:10:42.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-Is someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:47.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Answer! Do you want to pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:49.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:51.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:54.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You must not answer, Master Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:55.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Myoga?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.08,0:10:58.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you followed us, Old Myoga?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:00.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought he ran away\na long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:01.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And so I shall after this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:04.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not too late.\NTurn back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:06.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you babbling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.32,0:11:07.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you want to pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:10.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:14.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,'Course I want to pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.76,0:11:17.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why I came all the way here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:19.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,N-No, Master Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:22.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then you may pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:30.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-The stone {\i1}statues....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:56.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Wha...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:12:00.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They are Gozu and Mezu,\nthe guards of this gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:03.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They weren't just stone decorations?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:07.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Only the dead can pass through\nthese gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.05,0:12:12.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We make certain all those who wish\nto pass are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:17.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you won't let us pass\nunless we die?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:21.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now we know why Hakudoshi\nlured us here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:22.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:25.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That won't make me\nturn back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:31.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}These guys are big, but\nthat makes 'em slow!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.61,0:12:32.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:44.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did he succeed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:12:58.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Wha...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:00.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My Wind Scar didn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:02.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:05.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We cannot be slain by\nblades of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:10.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cannot be slain by\N"blades of this world"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:13.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is because Gozu and Mezu\nare not of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:17.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tetsusaiga is a sword that slays\ndemons of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:20.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it won't hurt Gozu or Mezu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:22.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-Then what are we going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.56,0:13:24.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha is going to get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:25.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:28.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't there a way to\nstop Gozu and Mezu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.90,0:13:30.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Once Gozu and Mezu\nare awakened,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:33.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,they will not become dormant until\nthe gate has been opened, then closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:39.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To be it bluntly, until Master Inuyasha\nhas passed through the gate as the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.41,0:13:40.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:42.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pass....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:44.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:50.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no point unless\NI'm alive!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:58.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In order to pass through the gate\nat the border of this world and the next,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.99,0:14:01.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,one must battle the guards,\NGozu and Mezu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:06.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right now, Inuyasha should be\nfighting them in my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:12.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Soon, the gate will {\i1}open....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.54,0:14:14.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In whatever way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:18.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Only the dead can pass\nthrough this gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.55,0:14:22.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So die by our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:26.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Are those the only\nwords you can speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.96,0:14:32.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not even a crack!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:37.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:43.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:47.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Swords of this world\nwill not harm us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:54.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:57.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If swords won't work,\nhow about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:14:59.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.57,0:15:20.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you want to pass through, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:22.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Tunnel doesn't work either!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.84,0:15:23.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H-How can that be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.35,0:15:32.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku! Hold that Wind Tunnel open!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:44.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:45.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.43,0:15:47.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I just tripped {\i1}'em....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:50.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:52.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:15:59.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:01.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even after using the Wind Tunnel\nto increase my speed,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.55,0:16:03.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}it didn't faze 'em.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:04.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:07.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Myoga?\NYou're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.42,0:16:09.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How can you say such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:11.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When I've stayed here without\nrunning away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:14.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,'Kay, I get it!\NSo hurry and speak up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:15.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, {\i1}yes....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:19.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Anyway, you just have to return\NMezu and Gozu to stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.90,0:16:20.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:24.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Gozu and Mezu will return to stone\nafter the gate has opened and closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:29.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So aim for the chains holding\nthe gate shut with your Wind Scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:31.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And now, I shall take my leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:32.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:35.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's running away, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:44.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Old Myoga is right, though.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.76,0:16:47.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I blast those chains apart\nand open the gate,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:49.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}it'll be like killing two birds\nwith one stone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.73,0:16:56.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My red Tetsusaiga\nthat breaks through barriers!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:58.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Awright!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:07.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:16.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:34.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good job, Inuyasha.\NI'm going on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:35.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura, why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.91,0:17:36.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.42,0:17:42.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It opened!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.49,0:17:46.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:55.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura, why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.96,0:17:56.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:02.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It opened!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:06.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:07.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:14.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:21.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demons have\nbecome {\i1}petrified....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:23.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-They couldn't {\i1}be....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:25.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hide or we'll turn to stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:26.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.13,0:18:27.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:55.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}There! Beyond the gate!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:03.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you want to pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.36,0:19:06.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:07.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:10.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who'd want to pass, idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:11.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:14.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We shall close the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:54.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:55.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uh-huh....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:01.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They've turned to stone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:03.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where's Kagura?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:06.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems she ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:10.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder if Hakudoshi\nknew about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:13.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That one turns to stone\nonce you pass the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:17.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He was testing {\i1}it....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:19.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,by using us and Kagura.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:36.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hakudoshi....you....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.49,0:20:39.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Kagura?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:42.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You could care less if I died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.46,0:20:46.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I heard that the living cannot\npass through the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:49.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I didn't know exactly\nwhat that meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.14,0:20:53.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't mess around with me,\nyou brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.88,0:21:05.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you in pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:11.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku just grasped your {\i1}heart....{\i0}\nfrom somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:16.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just remember this, Kagura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.23,0:21:20.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku and I are connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:23.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So think before you act\nnext time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:25.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.71,0:21:29.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd never be killed\nby the likes of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.11,0:21:35.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that true, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.45,0:21:37.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.72,0:21:40.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When the gate opened,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.42,0:21:45.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I sensed the presence of\nthe Sacred Jewel shard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:50.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So it's {\i1}there....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:55.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Somewhere over in that {\i1}world....{\i0}\nthe Sacred Jewel shard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.28,0:23:48.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,While we are in the Realm of Fire,\ndemons wreak havoc.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.68,0:23:50.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Someone is using birds\nto attack people.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.15,0:23:52.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you another one\nof Naraku's incarnations?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.05,0:23:55.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Saimyosho are proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.72,0:23:59.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't like to fight women,\nbut you're just too evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.46,0:24:03.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She seems to have something\nto do with {\i1}Naraku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.20,0:24:04.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but I don't think she's\nhis slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.90,0:24:09.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"The Fiery Bird Master, Princess Abi"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.94,0:24:12.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Impossible!\NShe countered the Wind Scar!
